			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The illusion of a fabulous treasure appears out of thin air. Your enemies throw aside caution to seize it.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Daily âœ¦ Arcane, Illusion, Implement, Zone</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Standard Action</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Area</b> burst 5 within 10 squares</p><p><b>Effect:</b> The burst creates a zone in its origin square. The zone lasts until the end of your next turn. You then make the primary attack. </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Primary Target:</b> Each enemy in the burst </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Primary Attack:</b> Intelligence vs. Will </p><p><b>Hit:</b> You pull the primary target up to 4 squares toward the zone. If the primary target is then in the zone or adjacent to it, the primary target is immobilized (save ends). </p><p><b>Sustain Minor:</b> The zone persists until the end of your next turn, and you make the secondary attack. </p><p>Published in Arcane Power, page(s) 105, Heroes of the Fallen Lands, page(s) 213. </p>",
